$version Hand-crafted Zybo Z7 vector fixture $end
$comment 4-bit LEDs vector, 2-bit RGB-LED position vector (named to match the led_rgb_ family prefix), 4-bit switches vector, 4-bit button vector (alias-driven match — 'button' is in the auto-bind alias table for 'btn'), HDMI in / HDMI out 24-bit pixel data, and 16-bit audio codec mic-in / headphone-out streams. Tests the auto-bind service's vector fan-out tier across the led / led_rgb / sw / btn families and validates singleton-slot binding for the four advanced peripherals. $end
$date 2026-05-04 $end
$timescale 1ns $end
$scope module top $end
$var wire 4 ! leds $end
$var wire 2 " led_rgb_ $end
$var wire 4 # sws $end
$var wire 4 $ button $end
$var wire 24 % hdmi_in_data $end
$var wire 24 & hdmi_out_data $end
$var wire 16 ' mic_in $end
$var wire 16 ( headphone_out $end
$upscope $end
$enddefinitions $end
$dumpvars
b0000 !
b00 "
b1010 #
b0000 $
b000000000000000000000000 %
b000000000000000000000000 &
b0000000000000000 '
b0000000000000000 (
$end
